{"tid":899393,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"珍奶拉麵「無媒苟合」","createTime":"2018-11-12T11:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T12:00:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99dc77a01d62ed59b43f2382f110505758a71281","tid":899393,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20181111/20543025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F20543025&d=v%2FI9KTCWvyXKTzwwpwON%2BWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8c4c5539\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F20543025&h=ea7a3050\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20181111/20543025</a><br />\n<br />\n珍奶拉麵「無媒苟合」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181111/large/e8903a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181111%2Flarge%2Fe8903a.jpg&h=d6e1b802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n極道ラーメン拉麵店fb圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n台灣「珍珠」即「粉圓」，是太白粉、木薯粉、地瓜粉等製成品，煙韌有嚼勁，口感豐富，令奶茶不止於奶茶。相傳在清朝慈禧年間曾作為進貢的獻壽禮，她老人家吃過讚不絕口，不過直到八十年代中期起，才成台灣飲料的主流，大受歡迎至今，他日塑膠粗飲管被取締，都不知怎麼順利享用了。<br />\n<br />\n奶茶之外，珍珠也出現在棉花冰、豆花、疏乎厘、蛋撻、奶黃包、雪糕、pizza、燉蛋&hellip;&hellip;中。最近，這黑色小粉圓還有新食譜，就是「珍珠奶茶拉麵」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣高雄一家拉麵店給「發明」的──也不算創新，只是「無媒苟合」。台灣損友道：「成了一時話題呢，2小時賣光。」<br />\n<br />\n我不以為然。也許只吸睛一陣，也有人特地光顧（因宣「限量供應」），相信不會長期紅火。<br />\n<br />\n首先台灣的奶茶不是真正「奶茶」，沒茶味，奶精充數，也沒奶味，加珍珠很配合，其實亦非上品，只一時解饞。那個湯底是奶茶，拉麵上的日式叉燒、筍、溏心蛋、青葱、紫菜、昆布、海苔、魚餅外，還加一把珍珠？格格不入。不知是鹹是甜，是正餐還是甜品。<br />\n<br />\n──我性格鮮明，最怕混沌、曖昧、亂倫的飲食。拉麵最重湯底，所以不會試。  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n特朗普勝利？ (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n金庸、梁羽生合論 (古德明)"},{"pid":"7ca0ebea1e861b3d565b0763282a4b301638f15e","tid":899393,"uid":149496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0171221472f42bfc9db630e73cdaa7eb78dc5774","tid":899393,"uid":67779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"哇屌，好撚嘔心呀"},{"pid":"e44a9d1f373b9025e62e9a6d781413d1793f5b23","tid":899393,"uid":199145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:41:57.000Z","msg":".....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee08b8d45903f9638e399cdf0e787034041f4355","tid":899393,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"狗糧"},{"pid":"c74ff59387b5e5e58b081ee34a8482688cbe876a","tid":899393,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3BH1KK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3BH1KK.png&h=9c9028da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sE0E3X6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsE0E3X6.png&h=a4550be6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcded0e534d7db4a2e9a70c1c06bc0aef03f6043","tid":899393,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}